public class CustomDomItemProviderAdapterFactory
extends DomItemProviderAdapterFactory

Factory that adapts DOM objects with Item provider adapters. For ISEIChildList and IWebServiceChildList it creates specific adapter for other DOM objects delegates to DomItemProviderAdapterFactory.
